Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 五月医生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 你不是阿久的……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.44,0:01:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是山田小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带点心过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可她不在病房
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复健告一段落后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和爸爸一起去洗交替浴了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs18}交替浴:将患部用冷水与热水交替地淋浴以防止浮肿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人不是她爸爸……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.84,0:02:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久的情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼 我不做了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亮 坚持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都这样 我已经受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.47,0:02:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要踢球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是因为交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从上个月开始在这做复健的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对一个小孩子来说确实很残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复健也是一个和疼痛的斗争啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是大人 因为疼痛和害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有很多人恢复到一定程度就放弃治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而久美却必须恢复到日常活动以上的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这关系着她以后能否还能继续她的创作事业
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何况伤到的是她惯用的手……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.30,0:03:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不害怕疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是她不怕疼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是 比起疼痛以后不能再做画的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对她来说才是压倒性的可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 小美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:23.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么又来了 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有好好做自己的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.70,0:03:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有做啊 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和老师一样在每件事情上都相当地努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今天有我的自信作品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么 小美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是糖煮牛筋和金橘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 这个 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(470,255)}味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.74,0:03:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浓浓的牛脂和金橘的水果味混合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想这种时候应该需要加点骨胶原
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.14,0:04:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有含丰富维生素C的金橘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.07,0:04:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像还能预防感冒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.12,0:04:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月医生不介意的话也来尝尝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 五月医生 请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山田小姐 让我从医学的角度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.14,0:04:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月医生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.07,0:04:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然营养很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不能胡乱的放在一个菜里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位小朋友要不要尝一尝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈要吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.46,0:04:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又出现新的牺牲者了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁去叫下救护车 啊 不 医院就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.04,0:04:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃 太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经空了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的料理好有人气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会再做给大家吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 山田 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢光临
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真高兴大家都喜欢我今天的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等一下 为什么你会这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然引起了一些小骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这说明大家很期待我下次的作品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次出远门的时候我会装视频电话的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.71,0:06:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理花 理花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么每天每天都不请自来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她今天没预定要跟你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且要商量的话在外面就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理花
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这个难缠的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚一定要来个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他弄清是非黑白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了理花也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了那个顶级秘密也好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是山田
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这些 竹本君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这些白色的瓷片粘在塔上会很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能派上用场就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来打算仍掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森 森田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老鼠在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都在找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.42,0:07:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止到底在哪……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听真山说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老鼠在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,西江福医院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公园旁那个很大的……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.37,0:07:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田 叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 森田 他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚是谁叫了森田的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是不是有人叫森田的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自把机器人模型放到网上拍卖的人就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁把这个家伙抓回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人简直就是菩萨转世啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么会突然……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么长时间都没在大家面前出现过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 他是怎么知道阿久的事情的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我拜托的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发信给真山让他帮忙找森田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真山现在在西班牙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久的事情本来是不想让他知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.51,0:08:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹本君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山田 别说什么抱歉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯独这个 你就饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田的样子怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我担心他会出事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹本君 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹本君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你……没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山田 请把自行车借我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算别人这么看我 就算被甩的机率是100%
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算看起来有多惨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算穷得连一朵花都买不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.18,0:09:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在受折磨的是她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.37,0:09:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛苦的是她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是我边说自己无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:32.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边顾影自怜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱头苦恼的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要有一个男人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.47,0:10:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我会慢慢地按下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1 2 3
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.29,0:10:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.23,0:10:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这点痛我还能忍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻醉 复健 我都不要做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是昨天那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 反正是治不好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要再受这种苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久 我们去外面走走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子能那样发泄也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久你也可以那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.46,0:11:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭也好 发脾气也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.58,0:11:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,治疗的路还很长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都憋在心里会受不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕这些话一说出口就停不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.56,0:11:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我一直这样给你添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会被阿修讨厌的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会讨厌你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:11:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前尿床的时候也是我照顾的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才说什么添麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被讨厌之类的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎也太晚了点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一坐车就晕车只好回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:15.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带你去河边又被河水冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管再发生什么 我都不会变了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会变的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.66,0:12:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.56,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕的不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果治不好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不能再画画的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:12:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生存的意义是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼吸 吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后还能干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 我真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能画画了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到死为止 还要活那么长的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.18,0:13:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.73,0:13:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候 曾经有一次 我见到了神
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这里没有纸和铅笔的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里还有什么意义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么多人中间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.14,0:14:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么生存下去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纸和笔一直都和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.79,0:14:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画画这事情 一直在保护着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有一天我得放弃做画了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会当场把我的生命还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.90,0:15:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回房间去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不想回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要不要喝些热饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 我确实与神立了誓约
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与我那个无法看见的神
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才会这么痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把这唯一一个誓约……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.43,0:15:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神 我现在……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.44,0:16:04.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竹本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.04,0:16:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚还在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是森田吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.02,0:16:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田知道了阿久受伤的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说要来医院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.72,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森田他……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.71,0:16:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥和我是这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你瘦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:55.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.75,0:16:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你突然就……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.61,0:17:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又去了很多地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.51,0:17:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又看到了很多东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:06.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创作了很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成了很多东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.39,0:17:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会画很多东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后又可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又可以画给你看了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要画了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不画也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.43,0:17:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不留下些什么就没有生存的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一句傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.28,0:17:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我活下来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.32,0:17:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异常温柔的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从他的口中溢出
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.38,0:18:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔的……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔却带着悲伤的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.50,0:18:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仿佛是呼唤着某个遥远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:24.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是我第一次听到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.26,0:18:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.38,0:18:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这种声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.80,0:18:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.78,0:18:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还会去什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.78,0:18:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是和森田在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 这个……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别告诉阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不打算让她知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算辞职吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从滨美大学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时离开一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直这样的话两方面都顾不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也会给大学里添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算先花三年时间照顾阿久的复健
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到她的白马王子却在这时候出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 如果阿久她……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择了森田吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.73,0:19:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,环游世界一次 两次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个很好的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这个世界 看到满足为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师 你为什么不对阿久说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对阿久
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说“选择我”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种话怎么说得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以为阿久付出你现在的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.83,0:20:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.63,0:20:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然知道没什么希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然知道完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我很认真的和她说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿久可能已经回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.36,0:22:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 请把你的人生交给我
